_sText: I made this map in 5 hours. This is uploaded for the PARTY PRINCESS PALACE server AKA best server ever. I touched up the original surf_buttes which hopefully will never see the light of day. This map is a fun freeform map (at least in my opinion). It is kinda crappily made but i like it. I get good fps but this map is pretty much impossible to optimize well. I actually had to turn the lightmap up to that it would compile without crashing. Yea....
